  "description": "Translation Keys Missing for Schedule-Related Content\n\nAdd missing translation keys for all schedule-related text strings in the application to ensure proper internationalization support.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify all hardcoded schedule-related strings currently not using translation keys\n- Create translation key entries with the \"schedule_\" prefix following the project's naming convention\n- Add translations for all supported languages in the application\n- Replace hardcoded strings with proper translation function calls\n- Verify all schedule-related UI elements display correctly in each language\n- Check for consistency with existing translation key patterns in the codebase\n\nAreas to verify:\n- Schedule creation and editing forms\n- Schedule display views (calendar, list, etc.)\n- Schedule-related error messages and validation feedback\n- Schedule status labels and action buttons\n- Time/date formatting strings specific to schedules\n- Schedule notification and reminder text",
